1. Test Group List
The following list includes 32 books historically attributed to Al-Ghazali.
Some of these works have been widely accepted as authentic, while others are considered pseudo-Ghazalian.
•	Al-Adab fi al-Din 
•	Al-Ajwiba al-Ghazaliyya fi al-Masa'il al-Akhrawiyya al-Madnun al-Saghir 
•	Al-Durra al-Fakhira fi Kashf 'Ulum al-Akhira 
•	Al-Hikma fi Makhluqat Allah 
•	Al-Iqtisad fi al-I'tiqad 
•	Iljam al-'Awam 'an 'Ilm al-Kalam 
•	Al-Kashf wa al-Tabyin fi Ghurur al-Khalq Ajma'in 
•	Al-Madnun bihi 'ala Ghayr Ahlihi 
•	Al-Mankhul min Ta'aliqat al-Usul 
•	Al-Maqsad al-Asna 
•	Al-Mawa'idh fi al-Ahadith al-Qudsiyya 
•	Al-Munqidh min al-Dalal 
•	Al-Qawa'id al-'Ashr 
•	Al-Qistas al-Mustaqim 
•	Al-Risala al-Wa'zhiya 
•	Al-Risala al-Ladunniyya 
•	Al-Wasit fi al-Madhhab 
•	Ayyuha al-Walad 
•	Bidayat al-Hidaya 
•	Fadaih al-Batiniyya 
•	Faysal al-Tafriqa bayn al-Islam wa al-Zandaqa 
•	Ihya' 'Ulum al-Din 
•	Khulasa al-Tasanif fi al-Tasawwuf 
•	Ma'arij al-Quds fi Madarij Ma'rifat al-Nafs 
•	Minhaj al-'Arifin 
•	Mishkat al-Anwar 
•	Mizan al-'Amal 
•	Qanun al-Ta'wil 
•	Qawa'id al-'Aqa'id 
•	Rawdat al-Talibin wa-'Umdat al-Salikin 
•	Risalat al-Tayr Dhikr al-'Anqa' 
•	Tahafut al-Falasifa 

2. Impostors Group Books
This list is organized according to the folder structure in the Run Environment/impostors_group directory, where each folder 
represents a specific author or impostor and contains their corresponding texts.
•	Author 1 – Abū Bakr al-Ṭurṭūshī
  o	Impostor 1 – Sirāj al-Mulūk
  o	Impostor 2 – al-Ḥawādith wa-l-Bidaʿ
•	Author 2 – Abū Bakr ibn al-ʿArabī
  o	Impostor 1 – al-ʿAwāṣim min al-Qawāṣim
  o	Impostor 2 – ʿĀriḍat al-Aḥwadhī
•	Author 3 – Ibn Taymiyyah
  o	Impostor 1 – al-Istiqāmah
  o	Impostor 2 – Majmūʿ al-Fatāwá
  o	Impostor 3 – Minhāj al-Sunnah al-Nabawiyyah fī Naqḍ Kalām al-Shīʿah al-Qadariyyah
•	Author 4 – Ibn Rushd (grandfather) 
  o	Impostor 1 – al-Bayān wa-l-Taḥṣīl
  o	Impostor 2 – al-Muqaddimāt al-Mumahhadāt
  o	Impostor 3 – Masāʾil Abī al-Walīd Ibn Rushd
•	Author 5 – Ibn Sīnā
  o	Impostor 1 – al-Shifāʾ: al-Ilāhiyyāt
  o	Impostor 2 – al-Qānūn fī al-Ṭibb
•	Author 6 – al-Juwaynī Abū al-Maʿālī
  o	Impostor 1 – al-Burhān fī Uṣūl al-Fiqh
  o	Impostor 2 – Ghayāth al-Umam fī Iltiyāth al-Ẓulam
  o	Impostor 3 – Nihāyat al-Maṭlab fī Dirāyat al-Madhhab
•	Author 7 – al-Fārābī
  o	Impostor 1 – Ārāʾ Ahl al-Madīnah al-Fāḍilah
  o	Impostor 2 – al-Ḥurūf
•	Author 8 – Ibn Khaldūn
  o	Impostor 1 – Riḥlat Ibn Khaldūn
  o	Impostor 2 – Tārīkh Ibn Khaldūn
  o	Impostor 3 – Tārīkh Ibn Khaldūn – Iḥyāʾ al-Turāth
•	Author 9 – Ibn Qudāmah al-Maqdisī
  o	Impostor 1 – al-Kāfī fī Fiqh al-Imām Aḥmad
  o	Impostor 2 – al-Mughnī
•	Author 10 – Ibn Rushd al-Ḥafīd
  o	Impostor 1 – Talkhīṣ Kitāb al-Maqūlāt
  o	Impostor 2 – Talkhīṣ al-Kawn wa-l-Fasād
  o	Impostor 3 – Bidāyat al-Mujtahid wa-Nihāyat al-Muqtaṣid – al-Bābī al-Ḥalabī
